3), Architecture Faculty in [[Taksim Square|Taksim]]]]\n[[File: Bogazici University.jpg|thumb|right|Faculty of Arts and Sciences, [[Bo\u011fazi\u00e7i University]] (1863), Istanbul]][[File:MarmaraUni.jpg|thumb|right|[[Marmara University]] (1883) campus life in [[Istanbul]]]]\n[[File:Ktu foto 1.jpg|thumb|right|[[Black Sea Technical University]] shore part of [[Kanuni]] campus, [[Trabzon]]]]\n[[File:\u00c7ankaya University Turkuaz campus.JPG|right|thumb|A view of [[\u00c7ankaya University]]'s campus, [[Ankara]]]]\n[[File:The Istanbul Ticaret University.jpg|thumb|[[Istanbul Commerce University]] Eminonu Campus near [[Golden Horn]]]]\n[[File:Iyte entrance gate.jpg|thumb|Entrance gate of [[\u0130zmir Institute of Technology]]]]\n[[File:Ytu 07.jpg|thumb|right|Main building of [[Y\u0131ld\u0131z Technical University]] (1911), Istanbul]]\n[[File:A picture of Campus.jpg|thumb|right|[[Kilis 7 Aral\u0131k University]], [[Kilis]]]]\n[[File:Gazi university.jpg|thumb|right|[[Gazi University]] in Ankara]]\n[[File:Merkez1.jpg|thumb|right|[[Hacettepe University]] in Ankara]]\n[[File:Mehmet Akif Ersoy University.jpg|thumb|right|[[Mehmet Akif Ersoy University]] \u0130stiklal Campus, [[Burdur]]]]\n[[File:Dil ve Tarih Co\u011frafya Fak\u00fcltesi Binas\u0131, Ankara.jpg|thumb|right|[[Ankara University]] Faculty of Languages, History and Geography]]\n[[File:Dokuz Eylul University Campus Entry Izmir Turkey.jpg|thumb|right|[[Dokuz Eyl\u00fcl University]] campus entry, [[\u0130zmir]]]]\n[[File:TrakyaUNI6.JPG|thumb|right|Rector`s Office and Convention Center [[Trakya University]], Edirne]]\n[[File:Erzurum-Atat\u00fcrk \u00dcniversitesi Kamp\u00fcs giri\u015f.jpg|thumb|right|[[Atat\u00fcrk University]] campus entry, [[Erzurum]]]]\n[[File:Mimarl\u0131k Fak\u00fcltesi.jpg|thumb|right|Architecture Faculty in [[Uluda\u011f University]], Bursa]]\n[[File:Om\u00fc - T\u0131p Fak\u00fcltesi.JPG|thumb|Hospital of [[Ondokuz May\u0131s University]]'s Faculty of Medicine in [[Samsun]]]]\n[[File:Pamukkale University Medical school.JPG|thumb|right|[[Pamukkale University]] medical school, [[Denizli]]]]\n[[File:OKANUNIVERITY.JPG|thumb|right|[[Okan University]] in Istanbul]]\n[[File:\u00c7U Beyazevler Campus.JPG|thumb|right|[[\u00c7ukurova University]] Beyazevler Campus in [[Adana]]]]\n[[File:I\u015f\u0131k 6931.jpg|thumb|right|[[I\u015f\u0131k University]] in Istanbul]]\n[[File:Balikesir Universitesi 1.jpg|thumb|right|[[Bal\u0131kesir University]]]]\n[[File:TOBB University of Economics & Technology.jpg|thumb|right|[[TOBB University of Economics and Technology]], [[S\u00f6\u011f\u00fct\u00f6z\u00fc]], [[Ankara]]]]\n[[File:Mersin University.JPG|thumb|Mersin University|[[Mersin]]]]\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Province !! University !! Type !! Founded\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Adana]]\n| [[Adana Science and Technology University]] || State || 2011\n|-\n| [[\u00c7ukurova University]] || State || 1973\n|-\n|| [[Ad\u0131yaman]]\n| [[Ad\u0131yaman University]] || State || 2006\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Afyonkarahisar]]\n| [[Afyon Kocatepe University]] || State || 1992\n|-\n|Afyonkarahisar University of Health Sciences\n|State\n|\n|-\n|| [[A\u011fr\u0131]]\n| [[A\u011fr\u0131 \u0130brahim \u00c7e\u00e7en University]] || State || 2007\n|-\n|| [[Aksaray]]\n| [[Aksaray University]] || State || 2006\n|-\n|| [[Amasya]]\n| [[Amasya University]] || State || 2006\n|-\n| rowspan=\"22\" | [[Ankara]]\n| [[Ankara University]] || State || 1946\n|-\n| [[Ankara Fine Arts  University]] || State || 2017\n|-\n| [[Ankara Hac\u0131 Bayram Veli University]] || State || 2018\n|-\n| [[Social Sciences  University of Ankara]] || State || 2013\n|-\n| [[Gazi University]] || State || 1982\n|-\n| [[Hacettepe University]] || State || 1967\n|-\n| [[Middle East Technical University]] || State || 1956\n|-\n| [[Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m Beyaz\u0131t University]] || State || 2010\n|-\n| [[Anka Technology University]] || Foundation || 2013\n|-\n|[[Ankara Medipol University]]\n|Foundation\n|\n|-\n| [[At\u0131