{"title_page": "2016\u201317 Cardiff City F.C. season", "text_new": "{{Infobox football club season\n| club          = [[Cardiff City F.C.|Cardiff City]]\n| season        = 2016\u201317\n| manager       = {{nowrap|[[Paul Trollope]]}}<br />''(until 4 October)''<br />{{nowrap|[[Neil Warnock]]}}<br />''(from 5 October)''\n| mgrtitle      = \n| owner         = [[Vincent Tan]]\n| chairman      = [[Mehmet Dalman]]\n| stadium       = [[Cardiff City Stadium]]\n| league        = [[2016\u201317 EFL Championship|Football League Championship]]\n| league result = 12th\n| cup1          = [[2016\u201317 FA Cup|FA Cup]]\n| cup1 result   = 3rd Round\n| cup2          = [[2016\u201317 EFL Cup|League Cup]]\n| cup2 result   = 1st Round\n| league topscorer   = [[Kenneth Zohore|Zohore]] (12)\n| season topscorer   = [[Kenneth Zohore|Zohore]] (12)\n| highest attendance = 23,153<br><small>(Vs. [[Newcastle United]], 28 April )</small>\n| lowest attendance  = 5,911<br><small>(Vs. [[Fulham F.C.|Fulham]], 8 Jan)</small>\n| average attendance = \n| prevseason  = [[2015\u201316 Cardiff City F.C. season|2015\u201316]]\n| nextseason  = [[2017\u201318 Cardiff City F.C. season|2017\u201318]]\n| pattern_la1 = _cardiff1617h\n| pattern_b1  = _cardiff1617h\n| pattern_ra1 = _cardiff1617h\n| pattern_sh1 = _cardiff1617h\n| pattern_so1 = _cardiff1617h\n| leftarm1    = 123BAA\n| body1       = 123BAA\n| rightarm1   = 123BAA\n| shorts1     = 123BAA\n| socks1      = 0000FF\n| pattern_la2 = _cardiff1617a\n| pattern_b2  = _cardiff1617a\n| pattern_ra2 = _cardiff1617a\n| pattern_sh2 = _cardiff1617a\n| pattern_so2 = _color_3_stripes_white\n| leftarm2    = FF0000\n| body2       = FF0000\n| rightarm2   = FF0000\n| shorts2     = FF0000\n| socks2      = FF0000\n}}\nThe '''2016\u201317 season''' was [[Cardiff City F.C.|Cardiff City]]'s 118th season in their existence and the 89th in the [[English Football League|Football League]]. Along with competing in the Championship, the club also participated in the [[FA Cup]] and [[EFL Cup|League Cup]]. It was [[Paul Trollope]]'s first season in charge since replacing [[Russell Slade]] as head coach.<ref>{{cite news |title=Cardiff City: Paul Trollope to succeed Russell Slade as first-team boss |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36319833 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=18 May 2016 |accessdate=18 May 2016}}</ref> Trollope was sacked on 5 October, whilst Cardiff were in the relegation zone, their lowest position in 11 years, and was replaced with [[Neil Warnock]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Cardiff City sack Paul Trollope as head coach |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37552009 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=4 October 2016 |accessdate=4 October 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Cardiff City: Neil Warnock named manager after Paul Trollope sacking |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37558965 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=5 October 2016 |accessdate=5 October 2016}}</ref> The season covers the period from 1 July 2016 to 30 June 2017.\n\n==Kit==\n<br>{{Fb_kit header\n|su=[[adidas]]\n|sp=[[Visit Malaysia]]\n}}\n|{{Football kit |pattern_la=_cardiff1617h|pattern_b=_cardiff1617h|pattern_ra=_cardiff1617h|pattern_sh=_cardiff1617h|pattern_so=_cardiff1617h\n|leftarm=123BAA|body=123BAA|rightarm=123BAA|shorts=123BAA|socks=0000FF|title=Home}}\n|{{Football kit |pattern_la=_cardiff1617a|pattern_b=_cardiff1617a|pattern_ra=_cardiff1617a|pattern_sh=_cardiff1617a|pattern_so=_bayern1617h\n|leftarm=FF0000|body=FF0000|rightarm=FF0000|shorts=FF0000|socks=FF0000|title=Away}}\n{{Fb kit footer|u=28 August 2016 |s=[http://www.historicalkits.co.uk/English_Football_League/season/2015-2016/championship.html Historical Football Kits] |date=July 2015}}\n\n==First-Team squad==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%; width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:blue; color:white; text-align:center;\"| No.\n! style=\"background:blue; color:white; text-align:center;\"| Name\n! style=\"background:blue; color:white; text-align:center;\"| Pos.\n! style=\"backg